the man from hong kong ( known in the u.s.a. as the dragon flies ) is a 1975 action film that marked the first &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; kong co-production filmed in both nations . it was directed by brian trenchard-smith and starred &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; jimmy wang yu and former 007 george lazenby . the film was later restored by the australian national film and sound archive .